### Specific Object [GET /readingRoom/objects/{id}] 

+ Parameters
    + id (number) - ID of the Object in the form of an integer

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id": 196,
                "name": "Real Academia de la Historia. Biblioteca",
                "authority_uri_lc": "http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n81124949",
