### Objects (Parameters) [GET /readingRoom/repositories?{country_id}=&{city_id}=&{city_id}=&{repository_id}=&{keyword}=&{name}=&{title}=&{lang}=&{type}=] 

+ Parameters
    + country_id (number) - ID of the Country in the form of an integer
    + city_id (number) - ID of the City in the form of an integer
    + repository_id (number) - ID of the Repository in the form of an integer
    + keyword (string) - Keyword to search all vHMML fields in the form of a string
    + name (string) - Name to search vHMML *Author Display Name*, *Scribe*, *Associated Names*, *Associated Names Display* in the form of a string
    + title (string) - Title to search vHMML *Title*, *Alternate Title*, *Contents Detail*, *Uniform Title* in the form of a string
    + lang (string) - Language to search vHMML *Languages* in the form of a string
    + type (string) - Type of Record. Values: **M (Manuscript)**, **P (Print)**, **A (Archival)**, **MP (Manuscript & Print)**, **NS (Not Specified)** 

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id": 118,
                "name": "Université Saint-Joseph. Bibliothèque orientale",
                "authority_uri_lc": "http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/no2002041068",
                "authority_uri_viaf": "https://viaf.org/viaf/126471052",
                "city_id": 861
            }
        ]